  "title": "SERVICE ADMIN EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><ul><li>Metrohm Singapore Pte. Ltd. – established in 1996 as a subsidiary of Metrohm Ltd, Switzerland world leader in chemical analysis instruments. We serve as Regional Support Centre for Asia and we provide the following analytical products and solutions: Auto-Titrators, KF, IC, Online Process Analyzers, TOC, NIRS, RAMAN, VA, CVS, Stability Measurement, Potentiostat/Galvanostat, PH/Conductivity meters, Monitor for Aerosols & Gasses in Ambient Air (MARGA) and other laboratory apparatus.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for a Service Admin Executive to support our growing service team. You will handle quotations, sales orders, customer coordination, and ensure smooth daily operations with the service team.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare accurate quotations, sales orders, invoices, and delivery notes to support sales and service processes</li><li>Process work orders and email orders, coordinating internally to ensure timely completion</li><li>Monitor service car stock levels and track work orders, purchase orders, and invoices to maintain operational efficiency</li><li>Follow up on customer requests and order changes to provide responsive customer service</li><li>Resolve order issues by communicating effectively with customers, colleagues, and the service team to maintain strong working relationships</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>1–3 years of experience in sales administration or customer service</li><li>Knowledge of Microsoft D365 CE is an added advantage</li></ul>",
